                <h1>UNC&#039;s Board of Governors rejects $5.3 million plan for Silent Sam amidst grading strike</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/17b5da0d-ccf5-47a4-baab-b6ce17f663e7.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Photo&#x20;from&#x20;a&#x20;protest&#x20;at&#x20;the&#x20;statue&#x20;before&#x20;it&#x20;was&#x20;pulled&#x20;down&#x20;by&#x20;protesters&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Photo from a protest at the statue before it was pulled down by protesters</p>

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
